    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a ride that\u2019s been truly loved? This beauty is in great shape and ready for its next adventure. It runs super smooth, the interior is nice and clean, and it\u2019s been incredibly reliable for me. It\u2019s the perfect mix of comfort and performance without the 'brand new' price tag. Come take it for a spin\u2014I promise you\u2019ll fall in love with how it handles!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
