      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking for a new home for my trusty ride! It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape, running smooth and ready for plenty more adventures. It\u2019s perfect if you're looking for something dependable that still looks great on the road. I've taken good care of it, and I'd love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
