      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L atmospheric inline-six. This engine retains its signature high-revving character with a recently serviced double-VANOS system and verified valve clearances. Power is channeled through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque vectoring. The chassis is structurally sound, featuring documented rear subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings to maintain the model's renowned handling precision. While the finish shows minor road-going patina, the performance remains uncompromising, with crisp throttle response from the individual throttle bodies and a neutral, communicative balance through the corners. A true driver\u2019s specimen ready for the backroads.",
